m har kj\u00f8rt flere d\u00f8gn uten hvile, det meste ser ut som om det er mindre overtredelser, sier Veglo."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|nordtrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "83f4414da13d1e448beb315367f589a79b6047e039b6b7671ea59588b74a81ca"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-28T03:42:56.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "P\u00e5 to m\u00e5neder hadde transportbedriften 234 brudd p\u00e5 kj\u00f8re- og hviletidsbestemmelsene."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1372525.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/veglo"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/46ae4ce483af987680ae4d6a2e10fb76ad95a934.jpg?5999ea2d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Fant 234 brudd under firmabes\u00f8k -adressa.no", "- Alvorlige brudd", "- D\u00e5rlige internrutiner", "- Mange misforst\u00e5elser", "Innser feil"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "46ae4ce483af987680ae4d6a2e10fb76ad95a934"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "careers"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "veglo milj\u00f8service as"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["alvorlig brudd", "sj\u00e5f\u00f8ren", "kj\u00f8re", "brudd"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["vegvesenet", "kj\u00f8re", "veglo milj\u00f8service", "hell", "veglo"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "nord-tr\u00f8ndelag"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["tove p. r\u00f8ddesnes", "arve veglo"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyhete